title: Ep 2554 - Tapu Sena On A Mission
shortDesc: Tapu Sena is on a mission to make this Ganesh Chaturthi festival the best ever so they divide the different tasks among themselves and the other members of the society. The ladies are assigned to the decorations

title: Ep 2555 - Water, Water, Everywhere
shortDesc: Gokuldham society members are excited to bring home Ganapati idol but nature wants to make the task difficult for them.

title: Ep 2556 - The Struggle
shortDesc: Bhide's dream seems to be coming true as due to heavy rainfall on the day of Ganesh Chaturthi, they are not able to get the statue to do the entire Pooja.

title: Ep 2557 - Dr. Hathi To The Rescue
shortDesc: When all seems lost due to the heavy rain as the Gokuldham Society members are not able to do the pooja, Dr. Hathi shows up with Gajanan's statue on his head and saves the day.

title: Ep 2558 - Tapu Senas Surprise
shortDesc: The Gokuldham society members thank Dr. Hathi for brining Gajanan's idol on the auspicious day of Ganesh Chaturthi.

title: Ep 2559 - Tappus Plan
shortDesc: What has Tappu Sena planned for the event? This is a question that's on Bhide's mind and he wants an answer as soon as possible, unaware that Tappu is yet to come up with a plan for the event.

title: Ep 2560 - Gearing Up For The Competition
shortDesc: After the announcement of various competitions during the celebration night, everyone in Gokuldham Society is gearing up for the contests. Jethalal is worried about being humiliated by Iyer so he calls up Goli at his house

title: Ep 2561 - Gokuldham Dhoomdham
shortDesc: The celebration of Gokuldham Dhoomdham begins and everyone is excited. Bhide inaugurates the event and then Tapu Sena takes over the stage and explains the various events and the rules.

title: Ep 2562 - And the Right Answer Is?
shortDesc: One by one, the Gokuldham society members take part in the activities organized by Tappu Sena.  Dr. Hathi and Komal turn the stage into a dance floor. Champaklal sings Vaishnava Jana To as Gandhi Jayanti is around the corner.

title: Ep 2563 - The Celebration Continues
shortDesc: The celebration of Ganesh Chaturthi continues in the Gokuldham society and everyone takes part in all the events of Gokuldham Dhoomdham event with full enthusiasm.

title: Ep 2564 - Taaraks Amazing Performance
shortDesc: Gokuldham Dhoomdham continues with some Q&A sessions and some amazing dance performances. Goli and Pinku fail to give the right answers to many questions but impress everyone with their hilarious dance.

title: Ep 2565 - Anxious Bhide
shortDesc: Another round of performances, another night of fun. Celebrations at Gokuldham continue in full swing. Tappu and his partner, Sonu, are called onto the stage to answer a set of questions. Bhide is anxious as Sonu is paired with Tappu.

title: Ep 2566 - Jethalals Turn
shortDesc: Finally, its Jethalal's turn for the question & answer round and Jethalal is ready with the answers that Goli told him. Fortunate enough for Jethalal, his partner is none other than Babita Ji.

title: Ep 2567 - Gandhi Jayanti Special
shortDesc: The Ganesh Chaturthi celebration finally comes to an end and everyone is sad after they let Gajanan go. Tapu Sena is ready with their next task which is the celebration of Gandhi Jayanti.

title: Ep 2568 - Surprise Awaits Jethalal
shortDesc: Babita has prepared a special dish for Jethalal but he isn't home. Feeling that he might miss out on Bengali cuisine for dinner, Jethalal tries to make it to Gokuldham as soon as possible, while Babita waits.
